                    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl mt-8 mb-6 color-copy">Building &amp; Scaling Businesses Since 1977</h2>
                    <p>A diversified investment firm based in New York, Trion partners with companies across <strong class="font-semibold">real estate, hospitality, and beyond</strong>—providing the expertise, network, and capital to unlock growth, create value, and position businesses for expansion or a successful exit.</p>
                    <p>For more than 45 years, we've invested in, acquired, and partnered with businesses ready to scale. Our approach blends <strong class="font-semibold">disciplined investing and operational expertise</strong> with a powerful network of industry professionals.</p>
                    <p>Our mission is simple: deliver the resources and guidance that allow entrepreneurs and operators to <strong class="font-semibold">work smarter, build faster, and create meaningful value—whether for long-term growth or a strategic exit</strong>.</p>
